u =\cos^3 x
du = -3\cos^2 x \sin x \;dx
dv = \cos x\;dx
v = \sin x
\sin x \cos^3 x + 3\int \sin^2x \cos^2 x \;dx
u=\cos ^{n-1}x,dv=\cos x dx
I_n=\int \cos^n xdx
I_n={\cos^{n-1}x\sin x}+(n-1)\int \cos^{n-2}x\sin^2 xdx
\sin^2 x=1-\cos^2x
I_n={\cos^{n-1}x\sin x}+(n-1)\int \cos^{n-2}x dx-(n-1)\int \cos^{n}x dx
I_n={\cos^{n-1}x\sin x}+(n-1)\int \cos^{n-2}x dx-(n-1)I_n 
I_n=\frac{\cos^{n-1}x\sin x}n+\frac{n-1}n I_{n-2}
n=4
\int \cos^4 x=\int{\cos^2x}\cos^2x\;dx=\int\left(\frac{1+\cos2x}{2}\right)\left(\frac{1+\cos2x}{2}\right)\;dx=\int\frac14(1+2\cos2x+\cos^22x)\;dx=\int\frac14\left(1+2\cos2x+\left(\frac{1+\cos4x}{2}\right)\right)\;dx
